<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1,user-scalable=0,minimum-scale=1, maximum-scale=1">
    <title>批量导入</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../../css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../../css/component.min.css">
</head>
<body class="ovfHiden qiao">

<div class="panel-body panel-body-shodow">
    <!--title-->
    <h2>工资发放</h2>

    <div class="info_middlebody">
        <div class="import_content" style="display: block">
            <div>
                <div class="content_top">
                    <h4 class="text-left">信息导入</h4>
                    <p class="text-left">1、根据模板中的批注，填写数据 <button  class="welfare_release_downbtn">下载模板</button></p>
                    <p class="text-left">2、上传填写后的数据文件<a href="#" class="file"><input type="file" class="welfare_release_upbtn" >上传文件</a></p>
                    <p class="text-left selected_file"></p>
                </div>
                <div class="content_mid">
                    <h4 class="text-left">导入说明</h4>
                    <p class="text-left">1、单次最多提交500笔</p>
                    <p class="text-left">2、单笔金额必须介于1.00元（含）到30,000.00元（含）之间</p>
                    <p class="text-left">3、手续费：0.5%</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="control-title">
                <div><span><a href="payroll_release_comfirm.html"><button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-zy btn-modeltwo">开始导入</button></a></span>
                </div>
                <div></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery-3.0.0.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/BusinessService.min.js"></script>
<script>

    //判断当前有没有上传文件
    addEventListener('load',function(){
        var selectThisfile=$('.selected_file').html();

        if(selectThisfile){
            $('#import_modelloading').attr('disabled',false)
        }
    },false)
</script>
</body>
</html>